 Law and Vice Principal for Internationalisation, University of Aberdeen.Claire Ralph, Head of Tax, Falklands Island Government; formerly Oil and Gas UK and HM Treasury.Uisdean Vass, Senior Counsel, Womble Bond Dickinson, Aberdeen.Emre Üșenmez, Lecturer in Law, University of Aberdeen.Constantinos Yiallourides, Teaching Fellow, University of Aberdeen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aNatural gasxLaw and legislationzGreat Britain. 0aPetroleum law and legislationzGreat Britain. 4aLaw. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Industries / Energy.2bisacsh1 aAldersey-Williams, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCowie, James, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGordon, Greg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGordon, Greg, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHavemann, Luke, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHunter, Tina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKemp, Alexander, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLatta, Steven, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPaterson, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPaterson, John, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRalph, Claire, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStephen, Linda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVass, Uisdean, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aYiallourides, Constantinos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÜşenmez, Emre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÜșenmez, Emre, eeditor.4edt4http:/